'''沙特新闻社'''（Saudi Press Agency，SPA，{{Lang-ar|وكالة الأنباء السعودية}}）又稱'''沙烏地新聞社'''、'''沙特通讯社'''，是[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]的官方[[新聞社|新聞社]]。沙特新闻社成立于1970年，是沙特阿拉伯第一家国家通讯社<ref name="rad">{{Cite web|title=Ministry of Culture and Information|url=http://www.saudinf.com/main/c6e.htm|accessdate=25 January 2014|work=SAMIRAD|archive-date=2014-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140115030153/http://www.saudinf.com/main/c6e.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。该社也是[[波斯湾|波斯湾]]地区的第一家[[新聞社|新聞社]]<ref>{{Cite book|last=Barrie Gunter|last2=Roger Dickinson|title=News Media in the Arab World: A Study of 10 Arab and Muslim Countries|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=89pMZd0JhDsC&pg=PA33|accessdate=8 February 2014|date=6 June 2013|publisher=A&C Black|isbn=1-4411-0239-6|page=33|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626230630/https://books.google.com/books?id=89pMZd0JhDsC&pg=PA33|dead-url=no}}</ref>。沙特新闻社由{{link-en|沙特媒体部|Ministry of Media (Saudi Arabia)}}负责，因此沙特新闻社負責人直接向部长匯報工作<ref name="rad" /><ref name="wan">{{Cite web|title=Saudi Arabia. Media market description|url=http://www.ihudaif.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/01/WORLD-ASSOCIATION-OF-NEWSPAPERS-%E2%80%93-WORLD-PRESS-TRENDS-2008.pdf|accessdate=16 May 2012|year=2008|publisher=World Association of Newspapers|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016050146/http://www.ihudaif.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/01/WORLD-ASSOCIATION-OF-NEWSPAPERS-%E2%80%93-WORLD-PRESS-TRENDS-2008.pdf|archivedate=16 October 2013}}</ref>。沙特新闻社用[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]和[[英语|英语]]发布新闻<ref>{{Cite web|title=Media landscape|url=http://www.menassat.com/?q=en/media-landscape/media-landscape-15|accessdate=4 June 2012|date=2007|work=Menassat|archive-date=2016-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324201200/http://www.menassat.com/?q=en%2Fmedia-landscape%2Fmedia-landscape-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。该社在[[波恩|波恩]]、[[开罗|开罗]]、[[伦敦|伦敦]]、[[突尼斯|突尼斯]]和[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]设有办事处<ref name=rad/>。

